{"tid":1856020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偽黃IGSHOP 食人血饅頭心虛del人留言","createTime":"2020-02-01T11:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T17:23:55.000Z","uid":755,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e1899a7767edfe4c662ecff1f513c662faa1e4f5","tid":1856020,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"利申:我係借朋友AC開post<br />\n呢間網店食人血饅頭，仲死雞撐飯蓋身有屎不斷Del人留言。<br />\n話說有日碌fb見到有得買酒精搓手液同濕紙巾咁就睇下啦，一睇嘩我冇眼花丫嘛，一支purell消毒液索價$128，出面賣緊$4x-$5x一支，再黎濕紙巾一包$128...<br />\n睇吓d留言一夜間已經好多人屌佢，話佢賣得比人貴成2倍幾，但佢竟然死撐話船運空運來貨價唔同會影響定價。<br />\n<br />\n因為愈來愈多人屌，最後佢del晒個幾個post，扮晒野話訂單超額已截單，唔係身有屎洗鬼del post？仲串過馬撚話：「唔通我用空運又要畫出腸。」笑撚死人咩想 一定係空運然後3月底先到貨啦，想呃邊個。有圖有真相：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpAqspQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpAqspQ.jpg&h=62c2fb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JP3d4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JP3d4R.jpg&h=2d561b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14z6Wib.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14z6Wib.jpg&h=93c37361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59rtqbx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59rtqbx.jpg&h=68068a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qmf2uDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmf2uDc.jpg&h=dc76a4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p